This paper deals with real-time style transfer on videos using semantic segmentation. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, it involves graphics (cs.GR) as it deals with styling and manipulating images. It also involves multimedia (cs.MM) as it deals with videos. The paper also uses deep learning techniques for semantic segmentation and style transfer, which falls under the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Lastly, the paper involves machine learning techniques for real-time performance, which falls under the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category.
